data.name: PP_AverageRequirementsByBusiness
PP_AverageRequirementsByFamily
data.value: SELECT M.Material,MB.Board,SC.[Date] AS DeliveryDate,CASE WHEN DATEPART(WEEKDAY,SC.Date) IN ({0},{1}) THEN 0 ELSE FLOOR(ISNULL(OpenQuantity,0)/{2}) END AS OpenQuantity FROM Sys_Calendar AS SC CROSS JOIN Sch_Materials AS M INNER JOIN Sch_MaterialBoards AS MB ON M.Material = MB.Material INNER JOIN Mfg_Boards AS Bd ON MB.Board = Bd.Board LEFT OUTER JOIN vw_Sch_WeeklyCustomerRequirements AS CR ON M.Material = CR.Material AND SC.[Week] = CR.[Week] INNER JOIN Sch_Business AS B ON M.Business = B.Business WHERE (('{3}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction) OR ('{4}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction)) AND SC.Date BETWEEN '{3}' AND '{4}' AND B.Family = '{5}' AND Bd.Volume='{3}';

data.name: PP_BoardCapacitiesByBusiness
data.value: SELECT M.Material,MB.Board,SC.[Date],ISNULL(SC.WorkingShifts,'') AS DayShifts,B.ShiftCombination AS BoardShifts,CL.Seconds FROM Sys_Calendar AS SC LEFT OUTER JOIN Sys_ShiftCombination AS SF ON SC.WorkingShifts = SF.Combination CROSS JOIN Sch_Materials AS M INNER JOIN Sch_MaterialBoards AS MB ON M.Material = MB.Material INNER JOIN Mfg_Boards AS B ON MB.Board = B.Board INNER JOIN Eng_1719Controls AS CL ON M.Material = CL.Material INNER JOIN Sys_ShiftCombination AS SFB ON B.ShiftCombination = SFB.Combination WHERE (('{0}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction) OR ('{1}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction)) AND (SC.[Date] BETWEEN '{0}' AND '{1}') AND M.Business = '{2}' AND B.Volume='Low';

data.name: PP_BoardCapacitiesByFamily
data.value: SELECT M.Material,MB.Board,SC.[Date],ISNULL(SC.WorkingShifts,'') AS DayShifts,Bd.ShiftCombination AS BoardShifts,CL.Seconds FROM Sys_Calendar AS SC LEFT OUTER JOIN Sys_ShiftCombination AS SF ON SC.WorkingShifts = SF.Combination CROSS JOIN Sch_Materials AS M INNER JOIN Sch_MaterialBoards AS MB ON M.Material = MB.Material INNER JOIN Mfg_Boards AS Bd ON MB.Board = Bd.Board INNER JOIN Eng_1719Controls AS CL ON M.Material = CL.Material INNER JOIN Sys_ShiftCombination AS SFB ON Bd.ShiftCombination = SFB.Combination INNER JOIN Sch_Business AS B ON M.Business = B.Business WHERE (('{0}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction) OR ('{1}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction)) AND (SC.[Date] BETWEEN '{0}' AND '{1}') AND B.Family = '{2}' AND Bd.Volume='Low';

data.name: PP_ByFamily
data.value: SELECT M.Material,M.Class,MB.Board,SC.[Date],DATENAME(W,SC.[Date]) AS WeekDay,ISNULL(Quantity,0) AS Quantity FROM Sys_Calendar AS SC CROSS JOIN Sch_Materials AS M INNER JOIN Sch_MaterialBoards AS MB ON M.Material = MB.Material INNER JOIN Mfg_Boards AS Bd ON MB.Board = Bd.Board INNER JOIN Sch_Business AS B ON M.Business = B.Business LEFT OUTER JOIN Sch_DailyProductionPlan AS PP ON M.Material = PP.Material AND SC.[Date] = PP.[Date] WHERE SC.[Date] BETWEEN '{0}' AND '{1}' AND B.Family = '{2}' AND (('{0}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction) OR ('{1}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction)) AND Bd.Volume = '{3}' ORDER BY M.Class,M.Material,SC.[Date]

data.name: PP_CommentsByBusiness
data.value: SELECT M.Material,MB.Board,C.Comment FROM Sch_Materials AS M INNER JOIN Sch_MaterialBoards AS MB ON M.Material = MB.Material INNER JOIN Mfg_Boards AS B ON MB.Board = B.Board INNER JOIN Sch_DailyProductionPlanComments AS C ON M.Material = C.Material AND MB.Board = C.Board WHERE (('{0}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction) OR ('{1}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction)) AND M.Business = '{2}' AND B.Volume='Low' ORDER BY M.Material

data.name: PP_CommentsByFamily
data.value: SELECT M.Material,MB.Board,C.Comment FROM Sch_Materials AS M INNER JOIN Sch_MaterialBoards AS MB ON M.Material = MB.Material INNER JOIN Mfg_Boards AS Bd ON MB.Board = Bd.Board INNER JOIN Sch_DailyProductionPlanComments AS C ON M.Material = C.Material AND MB.Board = C.Board INNER JOIN Sch_Business AS B ON M.Business = B.Business WHERE (('{0}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction) OR ('{1}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction)) AND B.Family = '{2}' AND Bd.Volume='Low' ORDER BY M.Material

data.name: PP_ByBusiness
data.value: SELECT M.Material,M.Class,MB.Board,SC.[Date],DATENAME(W,SC.[Date]) AS WeekDay,ISNULL(Quantity,0) AS Quantity FROM Sys_Calendar AS SC CROSS JOIN Sch_Materials AS M INNER JOIN Sch_MaterialBoards AS MB ON M.Material = MB.Material INNER JOIN Mfg_Boards AS B ON MB.Board = B.Board LEFT OUTER JOIN Sch_DailyProductionPlan AS PP ON M.Material = PP.Material AND SC.[Date] = PP.[Date] WHERE SC.[Date] BETWEEN '{0}' AND '{1}' AND M.Business = '{2}' AND (('{0}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction) OR ('{1}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction)) AND B.Volume='{3}' ORDER BY M.Class,M.Material,SC.[Date]

data.name: PP_MaterialsByBusiness
data.value: SELECT M.Material,M.Class,MB.Board,Bd.Class AS Tool, Bd.Volume,Bd.ShiftCombination,Seconds,Operators,M.CustomerPN,M.Description,B.Family,M.Business,StdPack,ISNULL(PastDue,0) AS PastDue,ISNULL(CI.Quantity,0) AS Stock,StartProduction,EndProduction FROM Sch_Materials AS M INNER JOIN Sch_MaterialBoards AS MB ON M.Material = MB.Material INNER JOIN Mfg_Boards AS Bd ON MB.Board = Bd.Board INNER JOIN Eng_1719Controls AS Cl ON M.Material = Cl.Material INNER JOIN Sch_Business AS B ON M.Business = B.Business LEFT OUTER JOIN vw_PastDue AS PD ON M.Material = PD.Material LEFT OUTER JOIN vw_CurrentInventory AS CI ON M.Material = CI.Material WHERE (('{0}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction) OR ('{1}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction)) AND B.Business = '{2}' AND Bd.Volume='{3}' ORDER BY M.Material;

data.name: PP_Daily_Plant
data.value: SELECT M.Material,Bd.Board,SC.[Date],DATENAME(W,SC.[Date]) AS WeekDay,ISNULL(Quantity,0) AS Quantity FROM Sys_Calendar AS SC CROSS JOIN Sch_Materials AS M INNER JOIN Sch_MaterialBoards AS Bd ON M.Material = Bd.Material LEFT OUTER JOIN Sch_DailyProductionPlan AS PP ON M.Material = PP.Material AND SC.[Date] = PP.[Date] WHERE SC.[Date] BETWEEN '{0}' AND '{1}' AND (('{0}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction) OR ('{1}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction)) ORDER BY M.Material,SC.[Date]

data.name: PP_Weekly_Plant
data.value: SELECT M.Material,Bd.Board,[Week],ISNULL(Quantity,0) AS Quantity FROM Sys_Calendar AS SC CROSS JOIN Sch_Materials AS M INNER JOIN Sch_MaterialBoards AS Bd ON M.Material = Bd.Material INNER JOIN Mfg_Boards AS Mb ON Bd.Board = Mb.Board LEFT OUTER JOIN Sch_DailyProductionPlan AS PP ON M.Material = PP.Material AND SC.[Date] = PP.[Date] WHERE SC.[Date] BETWEEN '{0}' AND '{1}' AND (('{0}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction) OR ('{1}' BETWEEN StartProduction AND EndProduction)) AND MB.Volume='Low' ORDER BY M.Material,SC.[Date]
